# Features and Task Sheet for OzusNews

## Core Features
- Modern Jetpack Compose UI
- MVVM and Clean Architecture
- NewsAPI.org integration
- News categories (e.g., Technology, Sports, Business, Health, etc.)
- Article details view
- Offline caching (Room)
- Bookmarking articles
- Light/Dark theme support
- Paging for news lists
- Image loading (Coil)
- DataStore for preferences
- Background sync (WorkManager)
- Dependency injection (Hilt)

## Task Breakdown

### 1. Project Foundation
- Initialize Android project with modular structure
- Configure Gradle for Compose, Hilt, Room, Retrofit, Paging, Coil, DataStore, WorkManager
- Securely store NewsAPI key

### 2. API Layer
- Define NewsAPI endpoints with Retrofit
- Create data models for articles, categories, etc.
- Handle API key securely

### 3. Data Persistence
- Set up Room database for articles and bookmarks
- Implement DAOs and entities
- Integrate Room with Paging 3

### 4. Domain Layer
- Define use cases for fetching news, bookmarking, etc.
- Create repository interfaces and implementations

### 5. Presentation Layer
- Implement ViewModels for news, bookmarks, categories
- Compose UI for news list, details, bookmarks, categories
- Navigation between screens
- Theme switching (light/dark)

### 6. Offline Caching
- Cache news articles locally
- Show cached data when offline
- Background sync with WorkManager

### 7. Bookmarks
- Add/remove bookmarks
- Display bookmarked articles
- Persist bookmarks in Room

### 8. Polish & Testing
- UI/UX improvements
- Unit and UI tests (JUnit, Espresso, Compose Test)
- Error handling and loading states
- Accessibility and responsiveness

### 9. Documentation
- Maintain starter_project_config and features/task sheet
- Add code comments and usage instructions